                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-113-off603 t18180114-113-crimeloc605"></join>, buying some things; I felt some person at my pocket, and missed my handkerchief; I turned round, and saw the prisoner walking away very fast; I collared him, and accused him of taking it; he said he had not got it - I insisted on searching him - He opened his arms, and it fell from under his left arm.</p>
